[5] Mexico (Estado de Chihuahua, Juarez)
Date: Sat 17 Aug 2019
Source: KTSM [edited]
https://www.ktsm.com/news/juarez/juarez-toddler-diagnosed-with-measles-in-citys-first-case-in-years/


A 2-year-old girl from Juarez has been diagnosed with measles in the city's 1st case in several years.

According to the Chihuahua Health Department, a sanitary fence was installed as doctors surrounded her home to check her family members.

Officials say Mexico has registered 7 measles patients -- now including one in Juarez -- this year [2019] after 20 years without any diagnoses.

